---
title: One-Pan Moroccan Chicken & Couscous with Pistachios & Lemon Garlic Crema
description: We’re all about that sauce, baby, and this North African–inspired meal has it in spades. The base of the skillet dinner is a saucy couscous simmered with carrots, onions, and dried apricots—for that craveable sweet-savory combo. Then there’s plenty of garlicky, lemon crema to drizzle over the Tunisian-spiced chicken. A scattering of crunchy pistachios at the end provides a delightful textural contrast. Moroccan? More like Mo’rockin!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-chicken-couscous-skillet-5b35a834.jpg
